1. First and foremost，the code implementation is Wrong. Without judging the result of any append, you should not assume that all the messages were added successfully. In my opinion, The support for batch messages (RocketMQ on DLedger) requires more rigorous consideration, and you can't split the messages and then call append API of DLedger simply. 
2. About code style . If you use IDEA, you can reformat code to pass the check style.
